title: Kaishain x Sumida Suizokukan Bikkuri! Kai Matsuri CM

alternative_titles.ja: 貝社員×すみだ水族館　ビックリ！貝まつりCM

synopsis: A Kaishain promotion for the Sumida Aquarium featuring a exhibit that has the species of animals the Kaishain characters are modeled after: clione, octopus, and various shellfish. The exhibit will run from Saturday, March 18, 2017 - Sunday May 7, 2017.
